Definition: Norwegian  HumanName. HL7 Norway. The profile adds the concept of middlename and further explains of the use for the data-elements in a Norwegian context.

Short: Defines a middle name as a specific extension as this is widely used in Norwegian names. The middlename is defined in norwegian legislation (lov om personnavn).
